Admin "0..1" -- "0..*" NewsArticle : authors >

' ── R17: Association — Admin manages FloodZone ──
Admin "1" -- "0..*" FloodZone : manages >

' ── R18: Association — User performs AuditLog ──
User "0..1" -- "0..*" AuditLog : performs >

' ── R19: Association — User is member of RescueGroup (via RescueGroupMember) ──
User "0..*" -- "0..1" RescueGroupMember : participates in >

' ── R20: Association — User is invited via RescueGroupInvite ──
User "1" -- "0..*" RescueGroupInvite : is invited via >

' ── R21: Association — User logs change in RescueRequestLog ──
User "0..1" -- "0..*" RescueRequestLog : logs change in >

' ============================================================
'  LAYOUT HINTS
' ============================================================

User -[hidden]down- RescueRequest
RescueGroup -[hidden]right- RescueRequest
Notification -[hidden]right- NewsArticle

@enduml
